commit 7c43adab6deb9302a24cc857c4aaa9b6b62215d2
Author: Chun-wei Fan <fanchunwei@src.gnome.org>
Date:   Mon Mar 12 16:43:53 2018 +0800

    CMake: Fix utility program installation
    
