commit 97145df2496f90e1ea4a41784f3224c60e973fd4
Author: Unknown <kunda@scribus.net>
Date:   Fri Nov 3 09:05:00 2017 -0400

    Trivial typos
    
    Found using `codespell -i 3 -w -I '../harf-whitelist.txt'`
    whereas the whitelist contents were:
    ```
    beng
    iff
    pres
    ot
    te
    teh
    ```

