commit 7dba30639a6f62803dfc21706bc7c654799f373e
Author: Behdad Esfahbod <behdad@behdad.org>
Date:   Thu Jun 1 11:44:42 2017 -0400

    Handle allocation failure in hb-language code

 src/hb-common.cc | 14 +++++++++++---
