commit 70202983f57fe85b2d3b56a9c205effeee66222d
Author: ebraminio <ebrahim@gnu.org>
Date:   Sat Feb 18 10:37:36 2017 +0330

    [ci] Disable vcpkg freetype installation and fix Appveyor CI (#422)

 appveyor.yml | 16 ++++++++--------
