    See https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1331339.
    
    Testcase: U+0BA4,U+0BC6,U+1133c,U+0BAA,U+1133c,U+0BC6,U+1133c
    
    * [indic] Add test for Grantha nukta that is allowed in Tamil by ScriptExtensions.txt

