commit e0f16a715bc3e621ff21a8be88102e9672630574
Author: Behdad Esfahbod <behdad@behdad.org>
Date:   Wed Feb 24 19:52:36 2016 +0900

    [ot-font] Towards accelerating get_glyph()

 src/hb-ot-font.cc | 23 ++++++++++++++++++++---
