Date:   Wed Jul 16 14:59:04 2014 -0400

    New API hb_buffer_add_codepoints()
    
    Like hb_buffer_add_utf32, but doesn't do any Unicode validation.
    This is like what hb_buffer_add_utf32 used to be until a couple
    commits ago.

