commit 75ec6d0bc5ca0170c73e4d1099a898d38d8f85c0
Author: Behdad Esfahbod <behdad@behdad.org>
Date:   Wed Apr 9 16:33:32 2014 -0700

    Tighten up check-static-inits.sh check
    
