Date:   Sat Jul 28 17:31:01 2012 -0400

    [GSUB/GPOS] Add get_coverage() and use it to speed up main loop
    
    And use it to speed up the hotspot by checking coverage directly in
    the main loop, not 10 functions deep in.
    
