Date:   Thu Feb 23 18:47:17 2012 -0500

    Remove unused hb_atomic_int_set()
    
    Apparently it can't be implemented on OS X.  We weren't using it anyway.

 src/hb-object-private.hh | 4 ----
 1 file changed, 4 deletions(-)

